						               													<description>Build - Destroy - Scheme&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Build the blueprints for Space Colony Hex: The Space Station of the future! Construct a wonderful new Space Colony with your fellow Engineers. But be careful, some of them are not who they claim to be. Prevent the Sneaky Con Artists from running away with all the money before the glorious Space Colony Hex is finished and stop the money-hungry Government Agents from bloating up the blueprints and making our sleek new Space Colony break the bank. Start scheming for Space Colony Hex's glorious completion or utter demise!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Space Colony Hex is a quick, tile-placement game with hidden teams. Players add tiles to the blueprint, bump other tiles off, and steal tiles from one another to achieve their hidden, sometimes shared, objective. The unique objectives will lead players to create makeshift alliances one minute then turn on each other the next. The ever changing blueprints will keep players on their toes looking for an opening to make the perfect move.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
